reviewText: Last year my daughter was crazy about this group. She inisted any more so she let her friend borrow it. Her friend loved it so much she didn't want to give it back so my daughter said she could keep it for a Christmas present. She was thrilled.

reviewText: Sent this product to my granddaughter and she seemed extremely happy with the birthday gift, so I'm going to give it a high rating.
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour

reviewText: I rate this item based on how excited and how much my young grand daughter loved the DVD,  Loved it very much, rated it a five based on how my times it has been viewed since receiving. Would recommend it to family and friends who have children that are crazy about 1 Direction. Received it in a very short time (from order date), very impressed.
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour

reviewText: Bought this item on a whim and just received it today and I LOVE it! The boys are adorable, the music is infectious (as long as you love boy band music) and the bonus 3 music video's are worth the DVD. The hype is there for a reason, these lads really do deliver and they do all that they can to make their fans happy.I look forward to their next DVD and their follow up CD to Up All Night.
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour

reviewText: My girls all loved this!  Now bear in mind they really like this group...so they appreciated it in a way I may not. They watched it over so many times, it's a good thing I can "appreciate" the music One Direction does.  As a mother I really love that the content is very appropriate for my kids, there are so many others groups that are not. BTW: The girls ages are 8 to 16.

reviewText: A gift for my niece.  She was so happy when she opened it.  I must say when we watched it, I also enjoyed it.  Very entertaining.
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour

reviewText: this is a great concert, especially on Blu Ray.  The picture quality could have been better, but it was recorded live in a small town in England.  If they had performed in Las Vegas in one of the great Casino theaters like Caesar's Palace, the picture would have been a lot better.  Still a great concert.
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour

reviewText: just like in the 80s, that was me with the nkotb shirt @ the nkotb concert screaming my head off!!:)  the 1D concert was very good, it was like you're right there in the arena!! the only critique i have is it was a lil' hard understanding the guys when they're talking in the extras and in between songs...their accents are so thick. (but who cares, i like it!)if you haven't had a chance to see 1D in concert, i agree with the other fans, this is the next best thing. to all of you seeing them on their tour..you're gonna have a blast!! and you'll never forget the concert!! i still remember the nkotb concert just like it was yesterday.
summary: if this doesn't make you a directioner, nothing will!!!
Title: Up All Night: The Live Tour
